name: Scary Deredere

Class: Deredere ***

"Cute or Scary Series" ***

You know those alien girls. When you look at them you often think - is she cute... or scary?! So, let's decide then! Each week we drop two types of cards with alien girls. By buying one you vote on them being Cute or Scary!
